Description: configuration manager for Unity desktop environment
 Unity Tweak Tool is a settings manager for Ubuntu Unity.
 It is a handy tool for  both power users as well as novice users
 and contains  most settings that any user might want to configure.
 It is simple, fast, well-designed and packed with plenty of useful features
 relevant to Unity and Compiz.
